        {
            "title": "阿里巴巴投資的月之暗面搶在DeepSeek之前發布新版人工智能模型",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 阿里巴巴集團投資的月之暗面更新了其旗艦人工智能(AI)模型，在外界預期DeepSeek即將發布新模型之際，加劇國內競爭。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">月之暗面周二發布聲明稱，最新版Kimi能夠在單條提示詞下同時處理文本、圖像和視頻。這與OpenAI、谷歌等行業領軍者推動的「全模態」趨勢一致。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">名為K2.5的新模型是過去一個月密集發布的一系列更新之一，顯示中國頭部AI公司競相在DeepSeek下一次發布之前搶占先機。DeepSeek近期預告將推出重大更新，其研究團隊已發表多篇論文，並在GitHub上發布代碼。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-5275b955-0fe5-395e-88d3-81d70b7738af-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">知情人士稱，隨著投資者對中國頂級AI公司的興趣再度升溫，月之暗面去年12月份從包括阿里巴巴和IDG Capital在內的投資者融資5億美元，該公司在募資後的估值達到43億美元。知情人士還表示，為了滿足投資者的需求，月之暗面已啟動新一輪融資，尋求最高50億美元的估值。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題China’s Moonshot Unveils New AI Model Ahead of DeepSeek Release</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Lulu Yilun Chen.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%98%BF%E9%87%8C%E5%B7%B4%E5%B7%B4%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%88%E4%B9%8B%E6%9A%97%E9%9D%A2%E6%90%B6%E5%9C%A8deepseek%E4%B9%8B%E5%89%8D%E7%99%BC%E5%B8%83%E6%96%B0%E7%89%88%E4%BA%BA%E5%B7%A5%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B-053214220.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-27 14:34:36",
